{"tid":678651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90公斤胖妹酒後鬧上吊　繩子不堪負荷先走了...","createTime":"2018-05-26T09:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T12:00:45.000Z","uid":1121,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0115e3d09ac2481118873c7083d59ac8ab59863e","tid":678651,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"命不該絕！中國溫州一名體型豐腴的少婦不滿老公單身赴任，日前在家一個人喝悶酒，喝著喝著越想越不對勁，一時想不開竟就在客廳上吊自殺，沒想到生死攸關之既，繩子突然「啪」一聲斷成兩截，少婦隨之重摔落地昏迷，鄰居聽到轟然巨響趕緊報警，最後少婦被警消人員送至加護病房急救，目前已無大礙。 根據中國《草根新聞》報導，承辦人員指出，少婦本身體重就有180斤（相當於90公斤），再加上用來自殺的繩子過細，推測是不堪負荷才斷裂，「居然有人會被身上的肥肉救了一命......。」少婦清醒後得知自己歷劫歸來，嚇得眼淚都噴了出來、直呼非常後悔，以後再也不敢做傻事了。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"8fae189b7d240ee3e5388c76611b4dd9ef2b9555","tid":678651,"uid":4525,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"條繩rip"},{"pid":"1ec03cf167e8d64655fe8fc006fe6e951cada3ec","tid":678651,"uid":121473,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f7996ab8b78f2c3b8022b0bb8bb188b4891f04","tid":678651,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"淘寶救佢一命"},{"pid":"73d3f151711befabd564dbc5ac87ef713358ffb0","tid":678651,"uid":185696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ec03cf167e8d64655fe8fc006fe6e951cada3ec","tid":678651,"uid":121473,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"笑咗"},{"pid":"bd8bece45939bfe7f5dc50e4be4b3f3e084588c6","tid":678651,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score